description:
The Windows 10 SDK Contract Files enables you to add Windows Runtime support to your WPF and Winforms apps.

      This package includes all the supported APIs up to Windows 10 version 1809.  If you are targeting earlier platforms, consider only offering functionality available on the detected platform version.  For further details, see:
      https://blogs.windows.com/buildingapps/2015/09/15/dynamically-detecting-features-with-api-contracts-10-by-10

      Supported platforms:
      - .NET Standard 2.0+
      - .NET Framework 4.6.1+
      - .NET Core 2.0+

      Requires default package management format set to PackageReference, and NuGet 4.0 or higher.
summary: The Windows 10 SDK Contract Files enables you to add Windows Runtime support to your WPF and Winforms apps.
